{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"This is a world-changing invention."},{"time":3000,"text":"The smoke alarm has saved perhaps hundreds of thousands"},{"time":6000,"text":"of lives, worldwide."},{"time":8000,"text":"But smoke alarms don't prevent fires."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"Every year in the USA, over 20,000 are killed or injured"},{"time":15000,"text":"with 350,000 home fires."},{"time":17000,"text":"And one of the main causes of all these fires is electricity."},{"time":21000,"text":"What if we could prevent electrical fires"},{"time":24000,"text":"before they start?"},{"time":26000,"text":"Well, a couple of friends and I figured out how to do this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29000,"text":"So how does electricity ignite residential fires?"},{"time":33000,"text":"Well it turns out that the main causes"},{"time":35000,"text":"are faulty and misused appliances and electrical wiring."},{"time":38000,"text":"Our invention had to address all of these issues."},{"time":42000,"text":"So what about circuit breakers?"},{"time":44000,"text":"Well, Thomas Edison invented the circuit breaker in 1879."},{"time":48000,"text":"This is 130-year-old technology,"},{"time":51000,"text":"and this is a problem, because over 80 percent"},{"time":54000,"text":"of all home electrical fires"},{"time":56000,"text":"start below the safety threshold of circuit breakers."},{"time":59000,"text":"Hmmm ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61000,"text":"So we considered all of this. And we realized"},{"time":63000,"text":"that electrical appliances"},{"time":65000,"text":"must be able to communicate directly"},{"time":67000,"text":"with the power receptacle itself."},{"time":69000,"text":"Any electrical device -- an appliance, an extension cord, whatever --"},{"time":73000,"text":"must be able to tell the power outlet,"},{"time":75000,"text":"\"Hey, power outlet,"},{"time":77000,"text":"I'm drawing too much current. Shut me off now, before I start a fire.\""},{"time":81000,"text":"And the power outlet needs to be smart enough to do it."},{"time":85000,"text":"So here is what we did. We put a 10-cent digital transponder,"},{"time":90000,"text":"a data tag, in the appliance plug."},{"time":93000,"text":"And we put an inexpensive, wireless data reader inside the receptacle"},{"time":97000,"text":"so they could communicate."},{"time":99000,"text":"Now, every home electrical system"},{"time":101000,"text":"becomes an intelligent network."},{"time":104000,"text":"The appliance's safe operating parameters"},{"time":106000,"text":"are embedded into its plug."},{"time":109000,"text":"If too much current is flowing,"},{"time":111000,"text":"the intelligent receptacle turns itself off,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and prevents another fire from starting."},{"time":116000,"text":"We call this technology EFCI,"},{"time":118000,"text":"Electrical Fault Circuit Interrupter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"Okay, two more points. Every year in the USA,"},{"time":123000,"text":"roughly 2,500 children"},{"time":126000,"text":"are admitted to emergency rooms for shock and burn injuries"},{"time":129000,"text":"related to electrical receptacles. And this is crazy."},{"time":133000,"text":"An intelligent receptacle prevents injuries"},{"time":136000,"text":"because the power is always off,"},{"time":138000,"text":"until an intelligent plug is detected. Simple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"Now, besides saving lives,"},{"time":144000,"text":"perhaps the greatest benefit of intelligent power"},{"time":146000,"text":"is in its energy savings."},{"time":148000,"text":"This invention will reduce global energy consumption"},{"time":151000,"text":"by allowing remote control and automation"},{"time":154000,"text":"of every outlet in every home and business."},{"time":157000,"text":"Now you can choose to reduce your home energy bill"},{"time":160000,"text":"by automatically cycling heavy loads"},{"time":162000,"text":"like air conditioners and heaters."},{"time":165000,"text":"Hotels and businesses can shut down unused rooms"},{"time":168000,"text":"from a central location, or even a cell phone."},{"time":171000,"text":"There are 10 billion electrical outlets"},{"time":174000,"text":"in North America alone."},{"time":176000,"text":"The potential energy savings is very, very significant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"So far we've applied for 414 patent claims."},{"time":184000,"text":"Of those, 186 have been granted:"},{"time":187000,"text":"228 are in process."},{"time":189000,"text":"And I'm pleased to announce that just three weeks ago"},{"time":192000,"text":"we received our first international recognition,"},{"time":195000,"text":"the 2009 CES Innovation Award."},{"time":199000,"text":"So, to conclude,"},{"time":201000,"text":"intelligent power can, globally, save thousands of lives,"},{"time":205000,"text":"prevent tens of thousands of injuries,"},{"time":207000,"text":"and eliminate tens of billions of dollars in property damage"},{"time":211000,"text":"every single year,"},{"time":213000,"text":"while significantly reducing global energy consumption."},{"time":216000,"text":"In the spirit of this year's TED Conference,"},{"time":218000,"text":"we think this is a powerful, world-changing invention."},{"time":221000,"text":"And I'd like to thank Chris for this opportunity"},{"time":224000,"text":"to unveil our technology with you, and soon the world."},{"time":227000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":228000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}